title: GarQuest
description: Gar and KO team up for a secret mission.

title: Manlier Fish the Fishlier Man
description: With the help of a conch shell genie, Man Fish upgrades himself in various ways to defeat the Warriors.

title: El dia divertido de Falafel
description: Cuando Falafel decide empacar sus cosas e ir a la ciudad, Manzana y Cebollín deben convencerlo de quedarse.

title: Pajama Pajimjams
description: Oscar pretends to be a talking pair of pajamas named "Jimjams" to make his friend Pajamas happy.

title: Crazy Mixed Up Puffs/Mizzen in Action
description: Crazy Mixed Up Puffs: The girls must literally work as one to try and stop Mojo from destroying Townsville./Mizzen in Action: Captain Crack McGraigen and his crew are tossed forward in time where discover the chemical X that marks the spot and it is up to the girls and Professor to send the super-charged pirates back to their own time.

title: Time Share
description: Batman and Blue Beetle have to travel back in time to stop Chronos from destroying a young Dark Knight on his very first case.

title: Terminal Velocity Part 1
description: While Windblade is away on a mission, Bee decides to relive a fun memory.

title: Babysitting Bedlam/Rubbed the Wrong Way
description: Rubbed the Wrong Way: After a Bakugan field errupts the town kids stampede to get their own Bakugan but when the field is contaminated Lia must save the day./Babysitting Bedlam: Dan and Wynton meet a strange boy who leads them into an underground maze where they discover the boy's Bakugan has been enslaved.

title: It Grows
description: As everyone celebrates Valentino for growing his first facial hair, a jealous Vic resorts to magical methods to grow a mustache and compete for attention.

title: Cheerleading
description: Brock drags Master Frown along to join him in following his dream, to become the Flyer on a cheerleading team. They team up with Unikitty & the gang and go head to head against Really Old Edith and her rival cheer team of meanies. But when the gang finds Brock is too heavy to be the Flyer they're forced to try a bunch of ridiculous ways to get him off the ground.

title: Zombie King
description: Grundy escapes his Louisiana prison intent on using a magical crystal which will allow him to raise the dead from their graves. Only Batman and Swamp thing stand in the way of his growing zombie army.

title: Infinity Train Trailer
description: What is the train? Where did it come from? And most importantly: What's in the next train car? Join Tulip, One-One, and Atticus in a mind-blowing adventure on the enigmatic Infinity Train.

title: The Big Trip
description: It's time for the gang's yearly vacation, but Hawk refuses to go, claiming the gang's vacations are never fun for him because the others are terrible at vacationing. Hawk only agrees to go if the gang pass his super-intense vacation training course.

title: Classic Rock
description: Batman thinks he's helping a homeless old man who is being mugged on the street only to discover that the man is a powerful wizard being chased by demons in disguise. It turns out the wizard is on a mission to save Shazam from the clutches of Black Adam.

title: Together Alone
description: Steven throws a party to bring his family together.

title: Aspirations
description: The Gangreen Gang is actually committing brilliant crimes. But behind every great gang, there has to be a great woman.

title: Brains TV
description: After a marathon of classic sitcom episodes, Clarence becomes stuck as alter-ego "Clarry," an obnoxiously overacting sitcom version of himself. It's up to his friends and family to help him snap out of it, or face life with a new Clarence.

title: Land of the Lost Shadows
description: When pieces of their shadows are stolen by a shadow demon, Uncle Grandpa and the gang must travel to the Land of Lost Shadows in order to retrieve them.

title: Hard Times in Silicon City
description: Mega Man must stop Blasto Woman from plundering the Museum of the Hard Age and its cache of military grade weaponry.

title: The Agent
description: Gumball and Darwin's clothes go missing after a swimming lesson and Gumball is forced to wear a tuxedo from the lost and found office. He believes it makes him look like a certain dapper British secret agent and, together with Darwin and Bobert (and far too many wisecracks) Gumball track down the villain responsible for stealing his clothes.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Memory Part 1
description: Windblade tries to help Bumbleebee but he is wary of this "stranger".

title: A Made Up Story
description: Someone is defacing all the posters and statues of Townsville with make-up. Can the girls stop this makeover takeover or will they get the blush off?

title: The Revolt
description: Darwin tries to highlight the plight of all the household objects he feels are being oppressed and maltreated by the uncaring residents of Elmore. He then decides to lead those objects in a revolt against the townspeople.

title: Anywhere but Sumo
description: When Clarence realizes Sumo has made a new group of friends at his new school, he becomes jealous and confused. Will Clarence accept a school life void of Sumo, or scheme his way into making their friendship work?

title: Astral Plane
description: Finn has an out-of-body experience that takes him all over Ooo and beyond.

title: The Wrath of Neddy
description: After Neddy the Mallet easily sails through all the obstacles in the Cave of Stuff he decides to stay as King Neddy, displacing the Cave Weirdos who beg the Warriors to help them reclaim their cave.

title: Career Day
description: After an excessive spending spree, the Golden Goose tells the gang it won't give them any more golden eggs until they learn the value of money. Following Rick's advice to save money, the gang open a cookie shop to make money on their own and save it in a huge vault.

title: La Leyenda del Parque Patinetas
description: Mientras buscan un parque de patinaje escondido, V y V se encuentran con una tribu de niños salvajes, que viven en una sociedad sin reglas ni adultos.

title: Tips
description: Apple and Onion have to find a way to ride the Hot Air Balloon which is in their town for one day only.

title: Road Trippin'
description: Realizing her and the Professor don't have much in common, Bubbles schedules a road trip with just the two of them.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Teletraan X Part 2
description: Investigating a signal in an abandoned missile silo, Bee and Windblade discover their computer back up drone Teletraan X, but it's a trap!

title: Mutiny for the Bounty
description: While Phil and Grandpa Max tune-up the Omni-Copter, a restless Ben takes the Rustbuggy off road, but when he is suddenly captured by Textrax and the hunter takes the bounty for himself, our hero must not only escape but avoid the wrath of the double-crossed Kraab and Sixsix!

title: Death Bear
description: Mordecai and Rigby want to get a picture in death bear's cage to impress Margaret and Eileen.

title: Gar Trains Punching Judy
description: With a big fight coming up, Punching Judy turns to KO and Gar to help her prepare.

title: Treasure Map
description: Uncle Grandpa and the gang don't have money to pay for their meal at a restaurant.  But when they discover a treasure map, it could be the answer to all their problems.  Too bad the treasure map is actually a restaurant activity placemat.

title: Snot and Tears
description: Robin tells the Titans to stop being reckless teens or the Creepy Catcher will get them.

title: Matrix of Leadership Part 1
description: With Windblade captured by the Seekers, Bumblebee is on his own for the first time and is responsible for saving Cybertron.

title: The Hands of Time
description: Master Wu mistakenly tries to single-handedly complete a battle he began decades ago against Acronix, one of the twin Hands of Time. But the arrival of the first Time Blade, a weapon with the power to speed up time, sends the Ninja to the Monastery just in time to rescue their master from certain doom.

title: The Mummy's Curse
description: The Baby Bears must return a mummy to its tomb or else they'll be cursed forever.

title: Innervasion Part 3: Strange Bedfellows
description: After the Junkbot shoots the Omnitrix and it begins glowing neon-blue, an imprisoned Vilgax explains it is now a gateway through which the Fulmini Empire will invade Earth, but the only way to stop them is from within the Omnitrix, so Ben must team up with the ultimate baddie if he is to save his planet.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Sugar Rush
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to pick up the donuts for the morning meeting.

title: #FightAtTheMuseum
description: Supergirl always relies on her strength, but she'll need more than brawn to stop brainy Catwoman from stealing valuable gems from the local science museum.

title: Whiteout Part 2
description: Windblade flies to the Himalayas to investigate while Bee watches television, acquiring new verbal "samples".

title: Buggy Out
description: After winning a Sumo Slammers Champion belt, Ben returns to the Rustbucket to find his prize in the arms of Kevin, but when his rival hijacks the Rustbuggy instead, our hero must stop at nothing to get back what's rightfully his!

title: #SweetJustice Part 4
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: Dog Daze/In Focus
description: Dog Daze: Lightning discovers a new Bakugan, Artulean, leading to an unhealthy rivalry with Howlkor./In Focus: While Lia's newswoman mom does an expose on the AO Strata the Hunter tries to capture Hydorous.

title: Last Laugh
description: Ben's fear of clowns emerges at an unfortunate time when our heroes stumble upon a wicked circus with a psychic vampire clown named Zomobozo.

title: The Price of Advice
description: After a paper origami fortune teller tells Izzy she's the world's best advice giver, she's determined to prove it.

title: Lil' Mac
description: Mr. Gus' nephew terrorizes Uncle Grandpa and Pizza Steve.

title: Innervasion Part 4: Mind over Alien Matter
description: While inside the Omnitrix, Ben and Vilgax must work together if they are to close the gateway, but once the Fulmini leader, the High Override, appears, even that might not be enough. Luckily, help arrives in the form of a being calling itself Glitch!

title: The Heart
description: When Mr. Robinson accidentally let slip how little he cares for Gumball and Darwin, they react by giving him the cold shoulder.  Surprisingly Mr. Robinson misses them and tries to win back their friendship. After a few failed attempts, Gumball and Darwin realize that Mr. Robinson's heart is protecting him, so they give it an intense affection overload.

title: The Babysitter
description: Vic & Val want to sneak out to a secret fireworks show but are thwarted when their new babysitter, Xochi, outsmarts them at every turn.

title: Lord of the Poppies
description: Grizz and the Poppy Rangers go camping on an island, but they soon find themselves deserted.

title: Escapism
description: Steven uses his psychic powers to find help.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: The Decisions
description: When everything goes wrong in Darwin's life, he begins to suspect that Gumball's bad influence might be to blame. Darwin decides to go elsewhere for guidance and finds a new mentor in Alan. But maybe it's time Darwin started making his own decisions.

title: Una epoca de traidores
description: Lloyd lucha con su papel como maestro en entrenamiento y Nya hace todo lo posible para reiniciar a Zane.

title: Project Ray Way
description: When Raymond starts his own fashion line, Rad and Drupe decide to make something even better.

title: Four by Four
description: During their visit to Twin City, Ben and Gwen sign up for some Laser Town awesomeness, but when Ben is teamed up with Kevin, the two must overcome their differences if they are to end up on top!

title: #SweetJustice Part 3
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: Cleaning Day
description: Victor & Valentino gain a newfound respect for cleanliness after Chata's house traps them inside its labyrinth of ancient, magical walls.

title: Sabotage Part 2
description: Shockwave creates false memories designed to convince Bee he was always a Decepticon spy.

title: Una linea en la arena
description: Jay lucha por defender la casa de su familia.

title: The First Day
description: Best friends Oscar and Hedgehog get dropped off at their first day at summer camp.

title: Teletraan X Part 1
description: The Decepticon Armada is nearing Earth to seek the Allspark and are desperate for clues.

title: Apple's in Trouble
description: Apple is challenged to a fight by a grumpy Cheesesteak, so he and Onion go on a quest to find the source of Cheesesteak's grumpiness.

title: Ragtag
description: When the kingdom runs out of inspiration, Unikitty takes it on herself to re-inspire the citizens with a riveting game of kickball where she and the gang form a ragtag team of underdogs, who are supposed to win a miraculous unexpected victory against Master Frown, Brock & The Doom Lords. But when the Doom Lords end up stinking at kickball, and the people are uninspired by the good guys' easy victory, Unikitty switches things up and joins the real ragtag team, The Doom Lords, to help lead them to a victory that finally inspires the kingdom.

title: Campfire!
description: The Titans put on a show but Robin warns that the performance must be boring or else they'll wake up the wolves.

title: Asteroid Blues
description: An asteroid is headed right for the kingdom, so Dr Fox leads the gang on a mission to save the kingdom by flying a rocket to the asteroid's surface and blowing it to bits with a huge bomb. But when they get there the gang finds the lonely asteroid is actually a super nice guy and don't want to blow him up.

title: Monstruos Bebes
description: Alice tienta a Oscar y a sus amigos monstruos para que asistan a un té festivo, pero el objetivo real es convertir a los monstruos en tiernos bebés.

title: Be Sweet
description: A fed up Lumpy Space Princess leaves the woods for a glamorous career in babysitting.

title: I Am Jethro
description: When a different kind of Jethro rolls off the assembly line, the plaza is in for some surprises.

title: Follow that Space Cab!
description: While Superman escorts his prisoner Mr. Mind between planets, he is attacked by Lobo who wants to collect a reward on Mind. Temporarily powered-down, Superman seeks Space Cabbie's help to get away from Lobo.

title: Tabes & Charlie
description: Tabes and Charlie team up to find Tabes' missing dog, Kirk.

title: Night of the Bat
description: Superman and other Justice League members have to battle Batman when he gets possessed by an evil Djinn, Uthool, who is intent on using the JL power core to blow a crack in Earth.

title: Return of the Honeysuckle Rangers
description: Craig discovers that the Honeysuckle Rangers have snuck into his side of the Creek to steal his most prized possession.

title: Mask of Power/Story Holes
description:
Mask of Power: Philomena Dusk from AAAnimus Corp. hires Magnus and gives him a control implant to bolster the power of his Bakugan to defeat Dan./Story Holes:  
A cryptic call leads the AO in search of a missing Bakugan but they soon realize the call was actually a test from a mysterious benefactor.

title: Familiar
description: With many changes going on in his life, Steven tries to find his place in the world.

title: The Pajama War
description: A Candy Kingdom slumber party devolves into panic when Finn and Princess Bubblegum vanish.

title: Cube Part 2
description: Windblade finds it hard to believe that Bee can't remember his favorite sport, Cube!

title: Legend of the Hidden Skate Park
description: While searching for a hidden skate park, V and V happen upon a tribe of wild kids, who live in a society without rules or adults.

title: The Extinction Event Part 2
description: Shockwave orders the Seekers to help him create an extinction event and destroy all organic life on the planet.

title: Etiquette Clarence
description: Clarence submits a short story into a creative writing contest, and he's overjoyed when he learns he's accepted as a finalist! But when Jeff finds out Clarence has to attend a formal dinner, he fixates on transforming the messy Clarence into a proper gentleman.

title: Panda's Birthday
description: For Panda's Birthday, the Bears try to help Panda meet his favorite K-Pop band, Monsta X.

title: Sabotage Part 1
description: From his lab on Cybertron, Shockwave launches an attack on Bee's most vulnerable place...his memories.

title: The Best VHS in the World
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to return an overdue VHS to the store so they won't be banned from renting new movies.

title: Chocolate Money Badgers
description: Oscar learns that he can earn merit badges that unlock prizes.

title: The Journey Part 2
description: The Autobots are nearly out of Energon, so they land on a dark planet where they encounter subterranean creatures.

title: Siloed Part 1
description: Windblade is playing Cube on Cybertron with Bee when she realizes these are memories and she is still held captive by Slipstream.

title: Cube Part 1
description: Bee discovers a mysterious object in the stolen Decepticon shuttle.

title: Arrested Development
description: Ben and Rook must stop the evil Robots from Dimension 12 while trapped in their own pre-pubescent bodies, thanks to Ben's childhood rival.  (Introducing Billy Billions.)

title: Lost in Time
description: Kai and Nya stow away aboard Krux and Acronix's time traveling snake mech in a desperate attempt to save Master Wu. But when they arrive in the past, they must help the Elemental Masters prevent the Hands of Time from literally re-writing NinjaGo history. Meanwhile, the the Ninja remain in the rapidly-shifting present trying to help Kai and Nya's father, who was hit with a Time Punch.

title: Pijamas Pijamas
description: Oscar finge hablar con unos pijamas llamados "Jimjams" para hacer feliz a su amigo Pijama.

title: I See a Funny Cartoon in Your Future/Octi-Gone
description: I See a Funny Cartoon In Your Future: The girls have the rare task of fighting a medium who is committing petty thefts./Octi-gone: When Bubbles finds a single leg of Octi's, she sets out to find out who took her toy and what they want from her.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Nice on Ice
description: An "unscheduled" TV appearance not only lands Aki in hot water for missing class, but sets Ice Man on a misguided mission to "unite" (i.e. freeze together) every human and robot couple in the city!

title: King of the Dinosaurs Part 1
description: With the help of Teletraan- X, Bee and Windblade excavate an deactivated Autobot that looks like a dinosaur.

title: Stockton, CA!
description: The Titans must find a way to keep all the Jump City residents from moving to Stockton.

title: Memories of Bobby
description: When a pillar of the Creek community leaves, our trio mourns their loss by remembering the good times.

title: Monster Party
description: Enid is faced with a choice when her old friends from Ghoul School show up.

title: Change Your Mind
description: Steven faces his biggest challenge yet.

title: Many Happy Returns
description: Gwen and Kevin pay Ben a surprise visit, but does Kevin's strange behavior have anything to do with an angry Tetramand princess, or her father's fleet of warships prepared to attack the Earth?

title: La ninera
description: Vic y Val quieren colarse en un espectáculo secreto de fuegos artificiales, pero su plan se ve frustrado cuando su nueva niñera, Xochi, los supera en todo momento.

title: Paseo en Buggy
description: Después de ganar un cinturón como campeón de Luchadores de Sumo, Ben regresa al Rustbucket y encuentra su premio en los brazos de Kevin. Pero cuando su rival secuestra el Rustbuggy, inuestro héroe no debe detenerse ante nada para recuperar lo que le pertenece legítimamente!

title: Matrix of Leadership Part 2
description: Bumblebee doubts his abilities as he has to find the Ark to awaken Optimus and the Autobots.

title: Malefactor
description: Khyber and his dog attacks Ben and Rook while they're at the "Olde Bellwood Days" festival, but does the hunter have other plans? (Introducing new Nemetrix alien Hypnotick.)

title: Secrets Discovered
description: Secrets are revealed as Nya confronts the Samurai X imposter, Kai pursues the truth about his parents and the other Ninja desperately seek to locate and rescue Master Wu. But as usual, some answers only lead to more questions.

title: Out of Commission
description: Mordecai and Rigby have one last day with the cart before they have to get rid of it.

title: Big Tick
description: A giant alien tick that sucks planets dry, lands on Earth with the sole purpose of destroying the planet and only a new alien hero can stop it.

title: Manzana esta en Problemas
description: Bistec con Queso, malhumorado, desafía a Manzana a una pelea. De ese modo, Manzana puede embarcarse con Cebollín en una misión para encontrar el origen del malhumor de Bistec con Queso.

title: Kevin 11
description: After a big argument with Max, Ben rebels by going out on his own in the Big Apple and makes friends with Kevin 11, who has plans for the Omnitrix.

title: A New Life
description: Apple and Onion both leave their homes and follow their dreams to the big city but things don't go quite to plan.

title: Carroneros
description: Lloyd se da cuenta de que hacerse cargo del debilitado Maestro Wu no es una tarea fácil.

title: Awaken Sleeping Giants Part 1
description: Bee, Windblade and Grimlock finally determine the location of the lost ship, the Ark.

title: Older
description: When Uncle Grandpa mistakenly transforms a young boy into a three-hundred-year-old man, he must manage to turn the kid back to normal before anyone gets hurt.

title: Blaze of Glory
description: Mega Man and Suna must overcome a sibling dispute over what to do on their day off in order to stop Fire Man from overheating the city.

title: #LaDulceJusticia - Primera parte
description: En el episodio estreno de cuatro partes de la serie, seis chicas comunes y corrientes se conocen y descubren que tienen poderes extraordinarios. Deciden unir sus fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: The Exit/The Lost and the Cost
description: The Exit: The AO compete with a rival Brawling team for ViewTube hits leading to a "winner take all" brawl./The Lost and the Cost: Everett Ray, a promotor, tries to get the AO to join an official league for Bakugan Battling.

title: The Mess
description: The boys stay up all night, even though the next day they're supposed to be babysitting Polly, Penny's little sister. They're so tired that they manage to lose Polly in the blink of an eye. They desperately look for her, but find themselves in increasingly weird situations every time they accidentally nod off.

title: The Hatching
description: The Ninja learn more about the Krux and Acronix, the two fallen Elemental Masters known as the Hands of Time, and are sure this threat has finally been eliminated. But with Wu out of action and suffering from the effects of the Time Punch, the Ninja discover a new enemy in their midst, the Vermillion Warriors. And the Ninjas have no idea who controls them.

title: La incubacion
description: Los Ninja descubren un nuevo enemigo en medio de ellos.

title: Camping is In Tents
description: A class camping trip turns into a treasure hunt while Harold is determined to catch Bigfoot and keep everyone safe.

title: Maccadam's Part 2
description: Windblade realizes Bee's memory must be coming back - they access the Hivemind and visit three different eras of Maccadam's.

title: The Perfect Team
description: Onion worries his relationship with Apple is in jeopardy when a stray cat enters the picture.

title: Allspark Part 2
description: They search for clues as to the whereabouts of the Allspark and uncover another important memory!

title: Scavengers
description: In the midst of an epidemic of mysterious metal thefts by the Vermillion Warriors, Lloyd realizes stepping up and taking over for the ailing Master Wu is not an easy task.

title: Saxophone Come Home
description: Oscar befriends a teenage Yeti.

title: #SweetJustice Part 2
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: King of the Dinosaurs Part 2
description: Teletraan-X's scans reveal their old friend Grimlock, who is intent on finding the rest of his missing dinosaur friends.

title: Fractured Part 1
description: Windblade discovers Bumblebee in the desert on his own.

title: Surely You Jest-O
description: House sitting for Omnibus is boring work for the Warriors, but their decision to allow Jest-O and his Taunting Jester Magisword come in from the rain to entertain them turns out to be their worst idea yet!

title: Legs from Here to Homeworld
description: Steven travels to visit family.

title: Huelga por el Botin
description: Mientras Phil y el abuelo Max afinan el Omni-Copter, Ben, inquieto, saca el Rustbuggy de la carretera. Pero cuando de repente es capturado por Tetrax, nuestro héroe no solo debe escapar, sino también evitar la ira de los traicioneros Kraab y SeiSeis.

title: Saltar del fuego a un mar hirviente
description: Kai y Nya son chantajeados para que usen sus poderes elementales combinados para salvar al Maestro Wu que se desvanece rápidamente.

title: Gotta Get Grup to Get Down
description: Grup hires the Warriors to help him become the biggest music star in Rhyboflaven, yet helping the little dragon achieve his big dream is no small task.

title: What's Opera, Titans?
description: Robin surprises the Titans with a trip to the opera but they soon fall asleep, and all dream about starring in their own operas.

title: Duncan Disorderly
description: Duncan escapes during a community walk only to discover he has to babysit Cody and Bridgette.

title: The Chupaca-bro
description: Team Tennyson discovers that a small village's goats are being terrorized by the legendary Chupacabra, but when Ben realizes it's actually Dr. Animo, our hero must thwart the dastardly doctor before he uses the essence of the goats to power up into an unstoppable form!

title: Siloed Part 2
description: Windblade manages to fight her way out when Slipstream is called away and she discovers Bee and Teletraan-X are there to help!

title: Introducing Kevin 11
description: At a local swap meet, Ben instead sets his sights on a Sumo Slammer collectible, but when Kevin takes it for himself, our hero must get it back by overcoming Kevin's secret weapon: an 11th alien!

title: #LaDulceJusticia - Tercera parte
description: Cuando seis chicas comunes y corrientes descubren que cada una tiene un poder extraordinario diferente, deciden unir fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis en la parte 3 del episodio estreno.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Sideline Dad
description: When the Girls start playing soccer, the Professor goes overboard.

title: Insignias de Choco Monedas
description: Oscar se entera de que puede ganar medallas al mérito que desbloquean premios.

title: Pausa y efecto
description: Kai se enfrenta a su padre solo para descubrir que sus padres son en realidad cautivos. Mientras tanto, los Ninja trabajan para liberar a Wu, Cyrus Borg y otros cautivos.

title: Megatron Is My Hero Part 2
description: Bee remembers an early version of Megatron where he was a gladiatorial hero, but realizes how dangerous he became.

title: On the Lam
description: Finn's dad Martin the Human fights for freedom on a strange new planet!

title: Megatron Is My Hero Part 1
description: Windblade explains the threat of Megatron and the Decepticons to Bee.

title: Innervasion Part 2: Call the Dream Police
description: After defeating the Warbot and discovering Vilgax inside, Ben's "secret voices" only worsen and begin affecting his sleep, but once Gwen discovers a sleepwalking Ben using missing items from the campsite to create his own massive Junkbot, it is up to Ben to stop his own creation.

title: The Perfect Adventure
description: When Mao Mao gets hungry for the perfect adventure, Adorabat tells a white lie.

title: Kelsey the Elder
description: A spat between the Elders of the Creek leaves an opening in their tabletop role playing game, so Kelsey joins the campaign!

title: Eruption Part 1
description: As the Autobots discover the Ark, they have to wake up their friends in this battle for the future.

title: The Attack
description: The Ninja celebrate their escape from the Vermillion Army and their retrieval of the Emerald Time Blade but with Acronix and Krux determined to get their Blade back, the Airjitzu Temple becomes a battleground.

title: El Equipo Perfecto
description: A Cebollín le preocupa que su relación con Manzana corra peligro cuando un gato callejero entra en su vida.

title: Showdown Part I
description: The Faction infiltrates Galvan in an attempt to destroy Azmuth.  (Introducing new Nemetrix aliens Omnivoracious & Vicetopus.)

title: El Primer Dia
description: Las familias de Oscar y Erizo, que son mejores amigos, los dejan en su primer día de campamento de verano.

title: Band of Outsiders
description: A gang of streetwise kids takes Baby Ice Bear under their wing.

title: Propinas
description: Luego de destruir por accidente el boleto de Falafel para un concierto, Manzana y Cebollín deben descubrir un modo de evitar la furia de Falafel.

title: Mother of All Cards
description: Chef attempts to trick the kids into making his mother gifts after he forgets Mother's Day.

title: Sour Candy Trials
description: Craig goes on a mind-bending journey as he tries to eat the most sour candy in the Creek!

title: The Journey Part 1
description: Bee accesses a memory from onboard the Ark on its journey from Cybertron to Earth.

title: Cheep Thrills
description: After finding a baby monster in the park, Bubbles insists on adopting it without considering the consequences!

title: Brotherly Love
description: After breaking Chata's plant, Vic and Val must accomplish the seemingly easy task of replacing it; this proves difficult when their squabbling puts Monte Macabre in jeopardy.

title: Shadowstriker Part 1
description: Bee doubts his fighting abilities as he continually loses in practice to Windblade.

title: Juntos Solos
description: Steven organiza una fiesta para reunir a su familia.

title: Piernas del Planeta Madre
description: Steven viaja para visitar a su familia.

title: Belson Gets a Girlfriend
description: Clarence is in disbelief when he learns his best friend Belson has a new girlfriend named Pipi. But when he observes their less than romantic behavior, he decides that he needs to teach them the ways of love to help keep their fling afloat!

title: Odd Bubbles Out
description: When Donny the Unicorn visits, Bubbles becomes jealous of his new friend.

title: Outbreak
description: When Dr. Psychobos steals a part out of the Omnitrix, causing chaotic side effects, it's up to Ben, Rook, and a small team of Plumbers get everything back to normal. (Introducing new Ben alien Kickin' Hawk, temp Ben alien Walkatrout, Upchuck Rook.)

title: Whiteout Part 1
description: Bee remembers his escape pod from the Ark crashed in the snowy Himalayas.

title: Jacob of the Creek
description: A terrible haircut forces Craig to go undercover at the Creek.

title: Pause and Effect
description: Kai confronts his dad for aiding the Hands of Time only to discover his parents are actually Acronix and Krux's captives. Meanwhile, as the Ninja work to free Wu, Cyrus Borg and the rest of the Hands of Time's captives, a third Time Blade arrives, one with the power to temporarily stop time!

title: The Oct-Father
description: When Princess Morbucks steals Octi, Bubbles' reaction surprises everyone, even her sisters.

title: Saxofon vuelve a casa
description: Oscar se hace amigo de un Yeti adolescente.

title: Allspark Part 1
description: Hiding from the Decepticons, Windblade use her Cityspeaker powers to search Bee's memory files.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Galactic Wonder
description: Wonder Woman has won student of the month at Super Hero High again!  As a special surprise Principal Waller has flown in Wonder Woman's mother, Queen Hippolyta, for a visit. Queen Hippolyta is not happy with what she finds and demands that Wonder Woman return to school at the island paradise of Themyscira. Hoping to take her mind off of her troubles with her mother Wonder Woman, Batgirl and Supergirl decide to investigate a strange electromagnetic anomaly. Their investigation leads them to the hideout of Lena Luthor where they discover a plot between her and Eclipso to transform the planet Earth into a new version of Gemworld!  The girls will have to split up to find the generators scattered around the planet and destroy them. They'll also have to overcome Lena's new breed of mood altering Kryptomites to save the day and convince Queen Hippolyta that Super Hero High is the best school for Wonder Woman!

title: Familiar
description: Con tantos cambios en su vida, Steven intenta encontrar su lugar en el mundo.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Eruption Part 2
description: Teletraan-X has to reboot the offline computer systems to wake up their Autobot friends and the ship while fighting the Deceptions.

title: Video Store
description: Clarence, Jeff, and Sumo visit their local video store to rent a movie, but discover it's all rented out! Each of them have a different idea of what tape to bring home, and must enlist the help of a tie breaker to figure it out.

title: A Time of Traitors
description: Kai's investigation of a Vermillion Warrior Helmet leads him to discover Krux is alive and well in NinjaGo, living under an assumed identity. Meanwhile, as the Vermillion Warriors go on a kidnapping spree, Lloyd struggles with his role as master-in-training and Nya does her best to reboot Zane, who was knocked off line in his first battle with the Vermillion.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Soother or Later
description: A terrified Duncan, who's afraid of lightning, learns it's even harder to break back into school than it was to break out when he finally escapes and finds himself in a dark alley with Izzy during a thunderstorm.

title: Out of the Fire and into the Boiling Sea
description: The Hands of Time blackmail Kai and Nya into using their combined elemental powers to retrieve the fourth and final Time Blade from the Boiling Sea with the promise the siblings can use its reversal power to save the quickly-fading Master Wu. Meanwhile, the Ninja and Cyrus Borg get unexpected help from Samurai X as they attempt to destroy the Hands of Time's time-travelling snake mech before it's operational.

title: Las manecillas del tiempo
description: El maestro Wu intenta completar una batalla que comenzó hace décadas contra Acronix.

title: #La dulce justicia - Cuarta parte
description: Cuando seis chicas comunes y corrientes descubren que cada una tiene un poder extraordinario diferente, deciden unir fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis en la parte 4 del episodio estreno.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Shadowstriker Part 2
description: Through memory, Bee is shown some of his past triumphs, like rescuing Optimus from Shadowstriker.

title: Amor de hermanos
description: Después de romper la planta de Chata, Vic y Val deben cumplir con la tarea aparentemente fácil de reemplazarla, lo cual demuestra no serlo cuando sus disputas ponen en peligro Monte Macabro.

title: The Extinction Event Part 1
description: Decepticons Shockwave and Shadowstriker arrive on Earth with a simple plan to find the Allspark.

title: #SweetJustice Part 1
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: Falafel's Fun Day
description: When Falafel decides to pack up and leave the city, Apple and Onion have to convince him to stay or they'll have to leave too.

title: The Longest Weekend
description: Muscle Man has to make it through a week without contacting Starla.

title: Secretos revelados
description: Los secretos se revelan cuando Nya se enfrenta al impostor Samurai X, Kai persigue la verdad sobre sus padres y los otros Ninja buscan desesperadamente localizar y rescatar al Maestro Wu.

title: Awaken Sleeping Giants Part 2
description: Slipstream and her Seekers engage in battle as our heroes trek towards the Ark.

title: Magical Moments: Week 5
description: This week's magical moment is...an exclusive new episode sneak peek!

title: Terminal Velocity Part 2
description: Bee finds himself on Velocitron with Hod Rod to have some fun but it turns into a nightmare as the Plague of Rust descends.

title: High Dive
description: Uncle Grandpa helps Samir overcome his paralyzing fear of the high dive.

title: #LaDulceJusticia - Segunda parte
description: Cuando seis chicas comunes y corrientes descubren que cada una tiene un poder extraordinario diferente, deciden unir fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis en la parte 2 del episodio estreno.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Mr. Moon/What's Wrong with Dan
description: Mr. Moon: Wynton finds a new Bakugan who proves difficult to control but things get more complicated when Col. Tripp seizes control of Trox./What's Wrong with Dan: With "Dan" behaving strangely toward the AO Lightning sniffs out the truth- an impostor!

title: Maccadam's Part 1
description: Bee and Windblade avoid an attack by Slipstream and Bee asks to go to Maccadam's!

title: Innervasion Part 1: Message in a Boxcar
description: As Team Tennyson prepares their boxcar for an upcoming race, Ben is hearing voices and is unable to go Upgrade to enhance his car, but once the race is interrupted by a mysterious Warbot, Ben must overcome the voices inside his head if he is to defeat the giant adversary.

title: Tripping the Light Fantastic
description: Mega Man tries to save Dr. Light from a date with "Mari," who's actually Hypno Woman in disguise!

title: I Love You Mao Mao
description: An explosive loner and his slacker best friend are waylaid from their journey into legend, only to find that their story is just beginning.

title: Fractured Part 2
description: Windblade realizes Bumblebee does not remember her and her mission to find the Allspark is critical.

title: A Line in the Sand
description: While the Ninja fight to save MegaMonster Amusement Park, Jay struggles to defend his family's home from the Vermillion Warriors. But the arrival of the Emerald Time Blade, with its ability to slow time, leads to a desert chase as the heroes try to reach the Blade before the snakes get it!

title: Forest Pirates
description: The Titans are at Super Hero Summer Camp for the week and they may need to add another teammate to win the big canoe race.

title: Monster Babies
description: Alice lures Oscar and his monster friends for a tea party, but only to turn the monsters into cute babies.

title: Like Water for Bimm
description: Vambre helps to get Bimm over her mission crippling fear of water.

title: El ataque
description: Los Ninja celebran su escape.

title: Running Wild
description: Student elections get blown out of proportion (literally) when Air Man lends his support to Aki's rival for class president, Peter Punk.

title: Gold Stars
description: Tree Trunks and Mr. Pig's child, Sweet P, runs into trouble on his first day of school.

title: Dia de limpieza
description: Victor y Valentino adquieren un nuevo respeto por la limpieza después de que la casa de Chata los atrapa dentro de su laberinto de paredes antiguas y mágicas.

title: Perdidos en el tiempo
description: Kai y Nya se escabullen en un intento desesperado por salvar al Maestro Wu.

title: Sun Scream/City of Frownsville
description: Sun Scream: The girls get the ultimate sunburn and must try to fight crime despite their UV damage./The City of Frownsville: When the tearful Lou Gubrious sets a crying ray on Townsville, the girls must find a way to stop the tears before the town is flooded.

title: Memory Part 2
description: Windlbade and Bumblebee are attacked by Decepticons and she regains his trust.

title: Una Nueva Vida
description: Manzana y Cebollín abandonan sus hogares y se mudan a la ciudad, donde se conocen por primera vez.
